1
00:00:34,180 --> 00:00:35,940
=The Embroidered Truth=

2
00:00:47,560 --> 00:00:48,359
Rulan,

3
00:00:49,320 --> 00:00:51,880
your handwriting is very
close to mine.

4
00:00:52,119 --> 00:00:54,079
(Shen Ruoheng, Lady Cheng'en)
But the writing on this seal,

5
00:00:54,520 --> 00:00:55,920
you must practice it again.

6
00:00:56,039 --> 00:00:57,039
Please be careful, My Lady.

7
00:00:57,280 --> 00:00:58,560
This is your personal seal.

8
00:00:58,719 --> 00:01:00,600
If someone uses it for evil,

9
00:01:00,600 --> 00:01:02,039
it could bring you trouble.

10
00:01:02,840 --> 00:01:05,040
My seal should never leave me.

11
00:01:05,400 --> 00:01:06,560
But if Rulan's identity

12
00:01:06,719 --> 00:01:08,799
is exposed because of this seal,

13
00:01:09,519 --> 00:01:11,120
everything will be lost.

14
00:01:19,079 --> 00:01:20,040
I understand.

15
00:01:21,239 --> 00:01:22,239
Then practice hard.

16
00:01:29,100 --> 00:01:31,900
(Ruoheng)

17
00:01:34,920 --> 00:01:36,439
(I bear a heavy burden.)

18
00:01:37,239 --> 00:01:40,280
(I will not neglect a single detail.)

19
00:01:40,580 --> 00:01:44,540
=Episode 17=

20
00:02:06,580 --> 00:02:08,260
(A Fine Gift from Cheng'en Manor,
Respectfully Presented)

21
00:02:12,460 --> 00:02:15,420
(A Fine Gift from Cheng'en Manor,
Ruoheng)

22
00:02:22,800 --> 00:02:25,280
(Ruoheng)
Wenyue, he's framing me again.

23
00:02:25,520 --> 00:02:26,439
What do you say?

24
00:02:26,919 --> 00:02:29,280
Your Highness, it's my fault.

25
00:02:29,719 --> 00:02:30,919
Please forgive me.

26
00:02:31,639 --> 00:02:33,080
Since the seal is real,

27
00:02:33,639 --> 00:02:35,759
let's drop this matter.

28
00:02:37,479 --> 00:02:38,439
Master Wu,

29
00:02:38,840 --> 00:02:40,240
aside from the Flower Festival,

30
00:02:40,840 --> 00:02:43,240
I don't want to hear any gossip.

31
00:02:43,879 --> 00:02:44,479
Yes.

32
00:02:47,159 --> 00:02:47,960
Ruoheng,

33
00:02:48,800 --> 00:02:50,599
you've been here a while now.

34
00:02:51,120 --> 00:02:52,319
How have I treated you?

35
00:02:52,840 --> 00:02:54,560
You've been very good to me.

36
00:02:55,599 --> 00:02:57,840
But I've upset you.

37
00:02:57,879 --> 00:03:00,360
Then I'll punish you by having
you walk with me.

38
00:03:12,039 --> 00:03:14,360
Do you know why I didn't
punish you today?

39
00:03:16,039 --> 00:03:17,400
Because you care for me.

40
00:03:20,439 --> 00:03:23,759
It's because no matter who you are,

41
00:03:24,400 --> 00:03:27,439
right now, you must be Shen Ruoheng.

42
00:03:29,319 --> 00:03:31,039
What do you mean?

43
00:03:33,039 --> 00:03:34,479
If after all this,

44
00:03:34,479 --> 00:03:36,680
I still couldn't see through you,

45
00:03:36,719 --> 00:03:39,039
I wouldn't deserve
to be the Princess Consort.

46
00:03:40,400 --> 00:03:42,000
I've been naughty lately.

47
00:03:42,680 --> 00:03:44,039
I've worried you.

48
00:03:45,639 --> 00:03:46,680
Do you know

49
00:03:46,800 --> 00:03:49,680
why I brought you to this
secluded place?

50
00:03:53,639 --> 00:03:54,840
It's quiet here.

51
00:03:55,080 --> 00:03:56,240
If you refuse to cooperate,

52
00:03:56,479 --> 00:03:58,120
I can still save your dignity

53
00:03:58,120 --> 00:03:59,639
and grant you a clean death.

54
00:04:02,039 --> 00:04:03,400
I don't quite understand

55
00:04:03,840 --> 00:04:06,000
what you're saying.

56
00:04:07,080 --> 00:04:08,479
The Prince returns soon.

57
00:04:09,199 --> 00:04:12,240
Please help me with wedding matters.

58
00:04:14,199 --> 00:04:15,680
It's good that you understand.

59
00:04:16,680 --> 00:04:18,240
I don't know how you

60
00:04:18,240 --> 00:04:19,439
bewitched Ruoheng,

61
00:04:19,879 --> 00:04:22,279
but without her help,

62
00:04:22,480 --> 00:04:24,000
you couldn't have gotten
the jade register

63
00:04:24,040 --> 00:04:25,839
or Yu Ming's support,

64
00:04:26,480 --> 00:04:28,079
let alone copy her handwriting

65
00:04:28,319 --> 00:04:30,279
with ninety percent accuracy.

66
00:04:30,920 --> 00:04:32,279
You're joking.

67
00:04:34,000 --> 00:04:35,839
Call it a joke if you like.

68
00:04:36,519 --> 00:04:38,600
But whoever treats you so well

69
00:04:38,920 --> 00:04:40,279
is your benefactor.

70
00:04:40,639 --> 00:04:42,800
If you make a mistake in my manor,

71
00:04:42,920 --> 00:04:45,000
you'll be offending that benefactor.

72
00:04:45,480 --> 00:04:48,079
Then how will you face your conscience?

73
00:04:48,800 --> 00:04:49,639
Wenyue,

74
00:04:50,199 --> 00:04:52,439
despite all of Wu Lian's schemes,

75
00:04:52,560 --> 00:04:53,639
I've proven myself innocent.

76
00:04:53,680 --> 00:04:55,240
You still don't believe me?

77
00:04:56,639 --> 00:04:59,240
You really are stubborn.

78
00:04:59,879 --> 00:05:00,759
Perhaps

79
00:05:02,199 --> 00:05:03,879
the Prince might actually like

80
00:05:03,879 --> 00:05:05,240
your stubbornness.

81
00:05:05,360 --> 00:05:06,079
But...

82
00:05:06,079 --> 00:05:06,800
Wenyue,

83
00:05:07,480 --> 00:05:09,680
your words today are very strange.

84
00:05:12,279 --> 00:05:14,439
I came to help you secure favor.

85
00:05:14,839 --> 00:05:16,240
If the Prince likes me,

86
00:05:16,439 --> 00:05:18,680
I'll see it as your blessing.

87
00:05:19,040 --> 00:05:20,560
If he doesn't,

88
00:05:20,720 --> 00:05:22,399
I'm yours to handle.

89
00:05:23,920 --> 00:05:25,360
Do you mean that?

90
00:05:25,639 --> 00:05:26,439
Yes.

91
00:05:29,519 --> 00:05:31,279
You look unwell today.

92
00:05:31,439 --> 00:05:32,240
Perhaps...

93
00:05:32,399 --> 00:05:34,240
Perhaps cut off her support completely.

94
00:05:43,519 --> 00:05:46,480
But the Prince returns soon.

95
00:05:47,279 --> 00:05:48,439
Won't this action of yours

96
00:05:49,279 --> 00:05:51,439
bring disaster upon yourself?

97
00:05:52,240 --> 00:05:54,439
I'm an honored guest at the manor.

98
00:05:55,319 --> 00:05:56,879
Who would suspect me?

99
00:05:59,079 --> 00:06:01,800
Besides, they're all fugitives
wanted by the city.

100
00:06:02,800 --> 00:06:04,800
Taking down their hideout now

101
00:06:05,600 --> 00:06:06,959
is perfect timing.

102
00:06:13,399 --> 00:06:14,959
Why not come in and sit?

103
00:06:15,879 --> 00:06:17,439
We still have

104
00:06:17,920 --> 00:06:20,560
so much left to say.

105
00:06:35,079 --> 00:06:36,399
What do you mean?

106
00:06:38,240 --> 00:06:39,720
Since we're about to become

107
00:06:39,720 --> 00:06:41,639
women serving one husband,

108
00:06:42,000 --> 00:06:43,279
I won't hide it from you.

109
00:06:44,399 --> 00:06:46,000
This is sterilization medicine.

110
00:06:46,720 --> 00:06:47,879
If you take it,

111
00:06:48,360 --> 00:06:50,439
it will prove that your words

112
00:06:50,839 --> 00:06:52,040
were sincere.

113
00:06:53,199 --> 00:06:55,680
(She fears I'll bear a son
and rival her.)

114
00:06:57,000 --> 00:06:57,639
What's wrong?

115
00:06:58,600 --> 00:07:01,240
Do you still harbor disloyalty?

116
00:07:19,439 --> 00:07:20,800
It's good that you understand.

117
00:07:21,319 --> 00:07:22,800
In this manor

118
00:07:22,879 --> 00:07:24,360
and in Jinxiu City,

119
00:07:24,839 --> 00:07:26,480
if I want someone dead,

120
00:07:27,040 --> 00:07:29,199
they have no chance to live.

121
00:07:31,959 --> 00:07:32,759
Wenyue,

122
00:07:33,399 --> 00:07:35,319
I've taken the medicine.

123
00:07:36,319 --> 00:07:38,279
But I have one request.

124
00:07:39,680 --> 00:07:40,920
If you agree,

125
00:07:41,439 --> 00:07:42,800
I will have no more worries

126
00:07:43,279 --> 00:07:44,879
and follow your arrangements

127
00:07:45,199 --> 00:07:46,480
until the Prince returns.

128
00:08:00,120 --> 00:08:02,399
Go against Yanyu Embroidery House,

129
00:08:03,439 --> 00:08:05,040
and you'll suffer for it.

130
00:08:08,879 --> 00:08:09,680
Mr. Liu.

131
00:08:11,680 --> 00:08:12,560
Ms. Huang.

132
00:08:13,040 --> 00:08:14,040
I'm coming in.

133
00:08:14,920 --> 00:08:16,000
No use hiding.

134
00:08:17,120 --> 00:08:17,959
Mr. Wang,

135
00:08:18,240 --> 00:08:19,480
you're trespassing.

136
00:08:20,120 --> 00:08:22,079
I knocked, Ms. Huang.

137
00:08:22,079 --> 00:08:23,040
But no one answered.

138
00:08:23,519 --> 00:08:25,680
I'm here with Magistrate Yu's order.

139
00:08:25,879 --> 00:08:27,399
Magistrate Yu, by the
Princess Consort's decree,

140
00:08:27,720 --> 00:08:29,959
declares Lady Cheng'en innocent.
She has returned to the manor.

141
00:08:30,199 --> 00:08:32,440
Though your actions violated
imperial law,

142
00:08:32,799 --> 00:08:34,039
the circumstances warrant leniency.

143
00:08:34,519 --> 00:08:37,000
The Princess Consort notes your care

144
00:08:37,240 --> 00:08:38,639
for Lady Cheng'en
during her imprisonment,

145
00:08:39,200 --> 00:08:41,679
and with the Flower Festival near,

146
00:08:42,039 --> 00:08:43,159
she grants you amnesty.

147
00:08:44,039 --> 00:08:44,759
Really?

148
00:08:45,600 --> 00:08:48,159
Would I dare lie to you?

149
00:08:48,600 --> 00:08:49,440
Magistrate Yu said

150
00:08:49,720 --> 00:08:51,559
for everyone to return to
their posts.

151
00:08:51,639 --> 00:08:53,159
Xiaotao, Xiaojiu,

152
00:08:53,399 --> 00:08:55,440
go back to the manor
to serve Lady Cheng'en.

153
00:08:57,279 --> 00:08:58,200
What about Feng Da?

154
00:08:59,080 --> 00:08:59,879
Mr. Liu,

155
00:09:00,279 --> 00:09:02,279
the dead cannot be brought back.

156
00:09:02,720 --> 00:09:05,600
Take his body and bury it.

157
00:09:07,360 --> 00:09:08,039
Farewell.

158
00:09:17,000 --> 00:09:17,799
My Lady!

159
00:09:19,600 --> 00:09:20,519
You're all safe.

160
00:09:20,519 --> 00:09:21,000
Thank goodness.

161
00:09:21,360 --> 00:09:22,240
What about Mr. Liu and the others?

162
00:09:22,240 --> 00:09:23,799
All safe, don't worry.

163
00:09:24,440 --> 00:09:27,399
But Ms. Huang's shop was trashed.

164
00:09:27,639 --> 00:09:28,720
If you hadn't returned,

165
00:09:28,919 --> 00:09:30,639
and Magistrate Yu released everyone,

166
00:09:30,679 --> 00:09:32,399
who knows how bad things
could have gotten.

167
00:09:33,480 --> 00:09:34,840
Is everyone else alright?

168
00:09:34,919 --> 00:09:36,000
No one was hurt.

169
00:09:36,720 --> 00:09:37,519
Good.

170
00:09:38,639 --> 00:09:40,440
Remember this debt.

171
00:09:40,720 --> 00:09:42,080
We'll settle it later.

172
00:09:43,720 --> 00:09:45,080
Right now, we only need

173
00:09:45,080 --> 00:09:46,679
the list of girls Wu Lian violated.

174
00:09:46,840 --> 00:09:47,639
Then we can...

175
00:09:47,639 --> 00:09:49,440
Li Xiaoshou got the embroidery
map from our insider.

176
00:09:49,679 --> 00:09:50,519
He's already searching.

177
00:09:52,080 --> 00:09:52,639
Good.

178
00:09:53,200 --> 00:09:54,759
All good news today.

179
00:09:55,200 --> 00:09:57,039
Then why do you look unhappy?

180
00:09:58,879 --> 00:09:59,960
We're all fine,

181
00:10:01,240 --> 00:10:02,399
but Meng Wan...

182
00:10:02,639 --> 00:10:03,759
What about Meng Wan?

183
00:10:10,240 --> 00:10:12,159
Ms. Meng, don't wait.

184
00:10:12,600 --> 00:10:13,679
In this godforsaken place,

185
00:10:13,679 --> 00:10:15,080
no one's coming for you.

186
00:10:15,600 --> 00:10:17,360
If you were in a government jail,

187
00:10:17,440 --> 00:10:20,360
you could hope for a righteous
judge to clear your name.

188
00:10:21,679 --> 00:10:22,919
But in a place like this?

189
00:10:22,919 --> 00:10:23,840
My advice

190
00:10:23,840 --> 00:10:25,200
is to eat something.

191
00:10:25,799 --> 00:10:26,799
As they say,

192
00:10:27,360 --> 00:10:28,440
it's better to face death

193
00:10:28,519 --> 00:10:30,279
on a full stomach, right?

194
00:11:11,400 --> 00:11:14,360
♪Night fades before the dawn♪

195
00:11:14,600 --> 00:11:17,600
♪Old vows still guide my hand♪

196
00:11:18,800 --> 00:11:21,560
♪The past no longer binds♪

197
00:11:22,040 --> 00:11:25,760
♪My heart still shines through dust♪

198
00:11:26,200 --> 00:11:30,320
♪Silent blooms, unchanged heart♪

199
00:11:31,160 --> 00:11:34,040
♪Bare hands weave through the frost♪

200
00:11:34,400 --> 00:11:36,400
♪Shadows linger, rain returns♪

201
00:11:36,400 --> 00:11:40,480
♪Honor crowns my weary soul♪

202
00:11:40,880 --> 00:11:43,080
♪For your faith that never broke♪

203
00:11:43,280 --> 00:11:47,400
♪I shattered all the love I knew♪

204
00:11:48,280 --> 00:11:50,200
♪No regrets, no debts unpaid♪

205
00:11:50,200 --> 00:11:54,440
♪At dusk I walk away alone♪

206
00:11:55,640 --> 00:11:58,120
♪If this tale becomes a storm♪

207
00:11:58,240 --> 00:12:00,880
♪Old shadows fade from sight♪

208
00:12:00,880 --> 00:12:03,480
♪One thought turns into ash♪

209
00:12:04,440 --> 00:12:09,800
♪No future left to write♪

210
00:12:10,880 --> 00:12:12,680
♪If I never fall♪

211
00:12:12,720 --> 00:12:15,080
♪How could this waiting end♪

212
00:12:15,080 --> 00:12:16,440
♪If I bear no scars♪

213
00:12:16,440 --> 00:12:18,760
♪How could I challenge fate♪

214
00:12:18,760 --> 00:12:21,120
♪I knew there was no way back♪

215
00:12:21,120 --> 00:12:25,120
♪Yet I left this hope behind♪

216
00:12:25,240 --> 00:12:27,360
♪For your faith that never broke♪

217
00:12:27,560 --> 00:12:31,520
♪I shattered all the love I knew♪

218
00:12:32,480 --> 00:12:34,400
♪No regrets, no debts unpaid♪

219
00:12:34,400 --> 00:12:38,800
♪At dusk I walk away alone♪

220
00:12:39,880 --> 00:12:42,480
♪If this tale becomes a storm♪

221
00:12:42,520 --> 00:12:45,080
♪Old shadows fade from sight♪

222
00:12:45,080 --> 00:12:47,440
♪One thought turns into ash♪

223
00:12:48,560 --> 00:12:53,800
♪No future left to write♪

224
00:12:54,680 --> 00:12:57,080
♪The lamp is out, you're gone♪

225
00:12:58,360 --> 00:13:00,480
♪Heaven and earth fall silent♪

226
00:13:02,160 --> 00:13:04,360
♪If we meet again someday♪

227
00:13:04,800 --> 00:13:10,600
♪This longing sleeps beneath the snow♪
